{"tid":1665923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再有人賴嘢...","createTime":"2019-10-20T17:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T18:01:27.000Z","uid":112875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43584fe28e8ac7bf9e8df2f7a70508f06270456f","tid":1665923,"uid":112875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代友出po</blockquote><br />\n我係今日係深水埗比人係高空掉裝滿天拿水既玻璃樽掉中既人<br />\n<br />\n想提返各位手足經過民居或者大廈都要小心 真係真係要擔遮 印象中呢排已經唔係發生唔只一兩次<br />\n<br />\n今次好彩冇中到頭 同埋只係裝滿天拿水既玻璃樽而唔係啲咩腐蝕性既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想見到有任何手足有事有意外<br />\n<br />\n另外想多謝返今日係呢件事幫左我既人 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49887a0709f52320cc07bc3654ac3cb1560cabc4","tid":1665923,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e27831b448fce7569ed4abe0ab0be08829580442","tid":1665923,"uid":112875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"事發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n深水埗元州街 大約7點幾<br />\n<br />\n比人係高空掉一個裝滿天拿水既玻璃樽 掉中博頭<br />\n<br />\n之後fa幫我洗左傷口call左白車<br />\n<br />\n白車幫我包左傷口 但我唔入急症<br />\n<br />\n之後有義診既人幫我縫傷口 邊個係邊到就唔講喇<br />\n<br />\n感謝香港嘅好心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}